title: Arnette Eyewear's Multiple Personality Disorder -- Skate -- Raleigh Road Trip
description:
Arnette Eyewear's skate team took the roads of Raleigh, North Carolina. Even though the weather didn't cooperate, the dudes still found ways to have a great time. Check out the shenanigans that the guys got into when the wheels started rolling and the beer got flowing. Thanks to all the homeys in Raleigh for showing how much fun you can have, even in bad weather.

Featuring exclusive skateboarding footage of Pat Duffy, Mark Appleyard, Willy Santos, Danny Supa, Luis Tolentino, Filipe Ortiz, Sierra Fellers, Scott & Ryan Decenzo. 

Music by:

Snakebit Drifters
"Wrong"

Rustangs
